- Yeah.

20
00:02:04,697 --> 00:02:06,190
How serious is it?

21
00:02:06,546 --> 00:02:07,604
Serious enough.

22
00:02:08,530 --> 00:02:11,125
I'd hate to lose
another partner just 'cause

23
00:02:11,605 --> 00:02:13,831
somebody's got a personal axe to grind.

24
00:02:15,790 --> 00:02:18,390
You think Chad
has something to do with it?

25
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:46,510
I got it.

26
00:02:46,810 --> 00:02:49,476
Listen... your business
is your business,

27
00:02:49,551 --> 00:02:52,152
and me bringing up my ex-husband
in the shower just...

28
00:02:52,697 --> 00:02:55,768
...that wasn't right,
so I'll never do it again.

29
00:02:57,098 --> 00:02:59,861
I didn't mean to break
your palm tree thing.

30
00:03:00,060 --> 00:03:01,800
My mom gave it to me.

31
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,820
I'm sorry.

32
00:03:04,884 --> 00:03:06,352
Where can I get you a new one?

33
00:03:06,465 --> 00:03:08,706
This cute little place in Palm Springs.

34
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,097
I think it's called a gas station.

35
00:03:16,890 --> 00:03:18,430
Listen...

36
00:03:19,260 --> 00:03:24,305
- I know things haven't been exactly...
- No, everything's all good, all right?

37
00:03:24,427 --> 00:03:25,890
I'll call you at the hospital?

38
00:03:28,130 --> 00:03:29,669
- All right.
- Be safe.

39
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:31,617
Give Rambis a hug for me.

40
00:03:32,140 --> 00:03:33,133
Okay.

41
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:54,790
I've got a dozen e-mails to return,
a conference call that starts like now.

42
00:03:55,001 --> 00:03:56,598
And the note says...

43
00:03:57,310 --> 00:03:58,334
What?

44
00:03:59,236 --> 00:04:01,087
You want me in Burbank by 8:00?

45
00:04:02,446 --> 00:04:04,500
That's in 20 minutes. I'm in Venice.

46
00:04:08,268 --> 00:04:09,298
Crap.

47
